STATE
v.
Donald Jay YOUNG. No. 468P13-3. Supreme Court of North Carolina. Dec. 15, 2015. Donald Jay Young, Tillery, for Young, Donald Jay. Amy Kunstling Irene, Assistant Attorney General, for State of North Carolina. J. Douglas Henderson, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 9th of November 2015 by Defendant to Appoint Counsel:

"Motion Dismissed as moot by order of the Court in conference, this the 15th of December 2015."
